data.title: Vibhavadi Rangsit
data.meta_description: Princess Vibhavadi Rangsit, née Princess Vibhavadi Rajani was a Thai writer and a member of the Thai royal family well known for her fiction writing and her developmental work in rural Thailand.
data.text:
This article is about the Thai princess. For the road, see Vibhavadi Rangsit Road.

Princess Vibhavadi Rangsit (Thai: วิภาวดีรังสิต; RTGS:Wiphawadi Rangsit; 20 November 1920 – 16 February 1977), née Princess Vibhavadi Rajani (Thai: วิภาวดี รัชนี; RTGS:Wiphawadi Ratchani) was a Thai writer and a member of the Thai royal family well known for her fiction writing and her developmental work in rural Thailand.
